    <title>EDITING: Forms - columns could not be hidden in a tablecontrol while editing a form</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Created attachment 91209
Form with a tablecontrol.</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">Try to hide a column while editing the form.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">Open the attached database.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">Open the form for editing.</sentence>
